## Workflow Commands Reference

| Command | Workflow | Output |
|---------|----------|--------|
| "Generate One-Pager for X" | Workflow 1 | ONE-PAGER-x-date.md |
| "Generate Spec for X" | Workflow 2 | SPEC-x-date.md |
| "Document feature X" | Workflow 3 | DOC-x-date.md |
| "Create PRD for X" | Workflow 4 | PRD-x-date.md |
| "Review document" | Workflow 5 | Consolidated feedback |

---

## Post-Document Generation Protocol

After generating ANY document in `documents/`, automatically execute this checklist:

### 1. Progress Tracking (required)
Update `pm-progress.json` (see `.cursor/rules/progress-tracker.mdc`)

### 2. Person Pages (if applicable)
If the document mentions people by name, check/create person pages in `context/people/`

### 3. Commitments (if applicable)
If the document contains action items with owners, add to `to_do's/commitments.md`

### 4. Next Step (via pm-coach Protocol 1)
Suggest next step per the capability map

**Rules:** Steps 1-3 are automatic (execute without asking). Step 4 follows pm-coach protocol.
